						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone set up in the temple of Durgā-Paramēśvari.</hi></p>						

						<p>Siṁghaṇa—A.D. 1236.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated in the <hi rend="bold">26th year</hi> of the reign of <hi rend="bold">Siṁghaṇadēva Manmatha, Phālguṇa ba. 10, Tuesday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1236, March 4, Tuesday.</hi> It states that a certain <hi rend="bold">Haripa</hi> died in the battle of <hi rend="bold">Ajjaḍi.</hi></p>						

